### Create new product transaction
POST http://localhost:3000/arlista
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "termek": "Hotdog",
  "vevo": "Kovacs Janos",
  "kategoriaId": 1,
  "egyseg": "db",
  "nettoar": 800,
  "mennyiseg": 2,
  "kiadva": true
}

